column3: 24-hour Volume Measures the total trading volume over the past 24 hours showing market activity and liquidity
Accumulation/Distribution Technical indicator that evaluates supply and demand by measuring the relationship between price and volume
Advance Decline Line Cumulative indicator showing the difference between advancing and declining issues in the market

Advance/Decline Ratio (Bars) Visual representation of market breadth showing advancing vs declining stocks as bars
Arnaud Legoux Moving Average Modified moving average that reduces lag and provides smoother signals
Aroon Measures the time between highs and lows over a time period to identify trend strength and direction
Auto Fib Extension Automatically plots Fibonacci extension levels to project potential price targets
Auto Fib Retracement Automatically draws Fibonacci retracement levels to identify potential support and resistance
Auto Pitchfork Automatically draws Andrews' Pitchfork tool to identify potential support and resistance levels
Auto Trendlines Automatically identifies and draws trendlines based on price action
Average Day Range Shows the average price range over a specified number of days
Average Directional Index Measures trend strength regardless of direction on a scale of 0 to 100
Average True Range Volatility indicator measuring the average range between high and low prices

Commodity Channel Index Measures current price level relative to average price level

Cumulative Volume Delta Shows the running total of volume traded at bid vs offer prices
Cumulative Volume Index Running total of advancing volume minus declining volume

Directional Movement Index Measures trend direction and strength
Donchian Channels Shows highest high and lowest low over a specified period
Double EMA Two exponential moving averages combined for faster response

column2: Ease of Movement Elder Force Index
column3: Ease of Movement Volume-based indicator showing the relationship between price and volume
Envelope Percentage-based bands around a moving average
Fisher Transform Converts prices into a Gaussian normal distribution
Gaps Identifies price gaps between trading periods
Historical Volatility Shows how volatile an asset has been over time
Hull Moving Average Reduced lag moving average that provides smoother signals
Ichimoku Cloud Multiple component indicator showing support resistance and trend
Keltner Channels Volatility-based bands using Average True Range
Klinger Oscillator Volume-based indicator comparing long and short-term money flow

Least Squares Moving Average Moving average calculated using linear regression
Linear Regression Channel Shows trend direction with parallel channels based on standard deviation
MA Cross Signals generated when two moving averages cross
McGinley Dynamic Modified moving average that adjusts for market speedup and slowdown
Median Shows the median price over a specified period
Momentum Measures the speed of price changes
Money Flow Index Volume-weighted RSI measuring buying and selling pressure
Moon Phases Shows lunar cycles for traders who consider astronomical influences
Moving Average Convergence Divergence Trend-following momentum indicator showing relationship between two moving averages
Moving Average Exponential Average giving more weight to recent prices
Moving Average Ribbon Multiple moving averages shown together to identify trend strength
Moving Average Simple Basic average of prices over a specified period
Moving Average Weighted Average giving different weights to different periods
Multi-Time Period Charts Shows analysis across multiple timeframes
Net Volume Difference between up volume and down volume
On Balance Volume Cumulative indicator adding or subtracting volume based on price direction
Open Interest Shows the total number of outstanding contracts
Parabolic SAR Trend-following indicator showing potential reversal points
Performance Shows percentage price change over time

Pivot Points Standard Calculates support and resistance levels based on previous period prices
Price Oscillator Shows difference between two moving averages as percentage
Price Target Projects potential price targets based on various methods
Price Volume Trend Cumulative volume indicator adjusted by price change percentage

Relative Volatility Index Indicates extremes in price movement

Rob Booker - Knoxville Divergence Custom divergence indicator

Rob Booker - Reversal Custom reversal indicator
Rob Booker - Ziv Ghost Pivots Custom pivot point indicator
RSI Divergence Indicator Shows divergence between price and RSI
Seasonality Identifies seasonal patterns in price movements
SMI Ergodic Indicator Modified stochastic momentum indicator

Smoothed Moving Average Moving average with reduced noise

Time Weighted Average Price Average price weighted by time

TRIX Triple exponentially smoothed moving average
True Strength Index Double-smoothed momentum indicator

Volatility Stop Stop level based on volatility
Volume Shows trading volume

VWAP Auto Anchored VWAP automatically anchored to significant points

Woodies CCI Modified Commodity Channel Index
